#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.cumprod.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.cumprod"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:1 of
msgid "Return the cumulative product of elements along a given axis."
msgstr "返回沿给定轴的元素的累积乘积。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:5 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the cumulative product is computed.  By default the "
"input is flattened."
msgstr "计算累积乘积的轴。默认情况下输入会被展平。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:8 of
msgid ""
"Type of the returned tensor, as well as of the accumulator in which the "
"elements are multiplied.  If *dtype* is not specified, it defaults to the"
" dtype of `a`, unless `a` has an integer dtype with a precision less than"
" that of the default platform integer.  In that case, the default "
"platform integer is used instead."
msgstr ""
"返回张量的类型，以及元素相乘时所用累加器的类型。如果未指定 *dtype*，则"
"默认为 `a` 的 dtype，除非 `a` 具有精度低于默认平台整数的整数类型。在这种"
"情况下，将使用默认平台整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:14 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape and buffer length as the expected output but the type of the "
"resulting values will be cast if necessary."
msgstr ""
"用于存放结果的替代输出张量。它必须具有与预期输出相同的形状和缓冲区长度，"
"但结果值的类型在必要时将被转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:19 of
msgid ""
"**cumprod** -- A new tensor holding the result is returned unless `out` "
"is specified, in which case a reference to out is returned."
msgstr ""
"**cumprod** -- 返回一个包含结果的新张量，除非指定了 `out`，此时返回对 out"
" 的引用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.doc.ufuncs`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:26 of
msgid "Section \"Output arguments\""
msgstr "“输出参数”部分"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:29 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:30 of
msgid ""
"Arithmetic is modular when using integer types, and no error is raised on"
" overflow."
msgstr "使用整数类型时运算是模运算，溢出时不会引发错误。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:34 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:45 of
msgid "The cumulative product for each column (i.e., over the rows) of `a`:"
msgstr "`a` 每一列（即跨行）的累积乘积："

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumprod.cumprod:51 of
msgid "The cumulative product for each row (i.e. over the columns) of `a`:"
msgstr "`a` 每一行（即跨列）的累积乘积："

